Question: One image shows a stack of two pillows with pointed corners, and the other image shows flat-edged pillows, with one pillow leaning against a pillow that is lying flat.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/wBEAAOSw5cNYVGHW/s-l300.jpg

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the pillows pointed corners?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the pillows pointed corners?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the pillows flat-edged?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the pillows flat-edged?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is one pillow leaning against a pillow that is lying flat?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is one pillow leaning against a pillow that is lying flat?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} xor {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
